"Singing my life with his words

1449
01:26:35,280 --> 01:26:36,952
[Boos and jeers]

1450
01:26:41,840 --> 01:26:43,831
[Guitar music begins]

1451
01:26:48,280 --> 01:26:51,750
[Sings] "Killing me softly with his song

1452
01:26:51,920 --> 01:26:53,592
"Killing me softly"

1453
01:26:53,720 --> 01:26:56,029
Who the hell is that?

1454
