"l felt all flushed with fever

1457
01:27:14,440 --> 01:27:17,955
"embarrassed by the crowd

1458
01:27:18,080 --> 01:27:23,359
"l felt he found my letters
and read each one out loud

1459
01:27:25,160 --> 01:27:28,630
"l prayed that he would finish

1460
01:27:29,120 --> 01:27:31,918
"but he just kept right on

1461
01:27:32,000 --> 01:27:35,629
"Strumming my pain with his fingers

1462
01:27:35,720 --> 01:27:38,632
"Singing my life with his words

1463
