1516
01:30:39,600 --> 01:30:41,397
Thanks, mate. Cheers.

1517
01:30:41,680 --> 01:30:44,911
RACHEL: How do you use this blender-thing?
WlLL: You don't.

1518
01:30:45,240 --> 01:30:47,754
MARCUS: I used to think two wasn't enough.
WlLL: Christ.

