1530
01:31:24,160 --> 01:31:26,674
So, listen, what's the deal
with you and Ellie now?

1531
01:31:26,760 --> 01:31:30,036
Is she your girlfriend?

1532
01:31:30,200 --> 01:31:31,872
Are you insane?

1533
01:31:33,960 --> 01:31:36,190
