1534
01:31:36,280 --> 01:31:38,919
-Why? What's wrong with them?
-Nothing.

1535
01:31:39,080 --> 01:31:40,195
What?

1536
01:31:40,880 --> 01:31:43,553
By the way,
I do think you and Rachel have a shot.

1537
01:31:43,640 --> 01:31:46,632
-I mean, if you don't screw it up.
-Thank you.

1538
01:31:49,160 --> 01:31:50,991
WlLL: I'd created a monster.

1539
01:31:51,280 --> 01:31:53,191
Or maybe he created me.

1540
01:31:55,960 --> 01:31:58,679
MARCUS: I don't know
what Will was so upset about.

1541
01:31:59,320 --> 01:32:02,869
